                  Sprecher/In:
                  %a{:href => "profile.html"} Patrick Frank
            .bottom-info
              .icon.arts
              .info-right
                %p.date 19:00 today
                %a{:href => "profile.html"}
                  %p.publisher Henrik Lafrenz
    .row
      %a{:href => "#"}
        %button More »
  %section#categories.yellow
    .row
      .container
        %h2 Categories
      #talk-collection{"data-equalizer" => ""}
        .category{"data-equalizer-watch" => ""}
          %a{:href => "explore.html"}
            .icon.politics
            %h3 Politics &amp; Society
            %p.lead Red-hot political topics and discussions about our society in the audio live stream or the archive. Listen to people who have a say.
        .category{"data-equalizer-watch" => ""}
          %a{:href => "explore.html"}
            .icon.science
            %h3 Sciences
            %p.lead Scientific lectures, panels and conferences in our virtual auditorium – listen live or download as podcast.
        .category{"data-equalizer-watch" => ""}
          %a{:href => "explore.html"}
            .icon.arts
            %h3 Arts &amp; Culture
            %p.lead News from the cultural scene, streamed live and made available in the audio archive. We let artists, critics and curators speak out.
        .category{"data-equalizer-watch" => ""}
          %a{:href => "explore.html"}
            .icon.tech
            %h3 Technology
            %p.lead Not only for geeks: technological progress concerns all of us. Listen to live streams or download the podcasts.
        .category{"data-equalizer-watch" => ""}
          %a{:href => "explore.html"}
            .icon.media
            %h3 Media
            %p.lead The media world is changing rapidly. Lectures and discussions about traditional media and digitalisation in the audio archive and in live streams.
        .category{"data-equalizer-watch" => ""}
          %a{:href => "explore.html"}
            .icon.business
            %h3 Business
            %p.lead Business conferences and company events offer interesting insights into economic developments and useful career advice.
  %section#publishers.white
    .row
      .container
        %h2
          Some of the distinguished Publishers
          %br>/
          on Voice Republic:
