        .publisher{"data-equalizer-watch" => ""}
          %a{:href => "profile.html"}
            %img{:alt => "", :src => "img/publishers/mosse.png"}/
            %h4 Mosse Lectures at Humboldt University
            %p.lead The lecture series “Mosse Lectures” at the Humboldt University in Berlin imparts knowledge on topics like history, politics, economy, arts and literature. The lectures can be listened to on Voice Republic.
